# 🎬 Movie List & IMDb Rating App

A web application that allows users to create their own movie lists, fetch IMDb ratings automatically, and browse movies by genre.

## 🚀 Features

- ✅ Add and manage a personal list of movies
- 🌟 Automatically fetch IMDb ratings for each movie
- 🎭 Browse or filter movies based on genre
- 🔍 Search for movies by title

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- **API**: IMDb or OMDb API (for fetching ratings and movie data)

